Package io.openhc.ohc.basestation.rpc.rpcs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Rpc
    Abstract parent for RPCs allowing for easy implementation of new RPCs
    Rpc_device_get_field
    This RPC requests information about a field from the basestation.
    Rpc_device_get_num_fields
    This RPC returns the number of fields on a device
    Rpc_device_set_field_value
    This RPC sets the value of a remote field on the basestation.
    Rpc_get_device
    This RPC returns a whole device object including all fields
    Rpc_get_device_id
    This RPC returns the internal alphanumerical id of a device
    Rpc_get_device_ids
    This RPC returns the internal alphanumerical ids of all devices
    Rpc_get_device_name
    This RPC returns the human readable name of a device
    Rpc_get_num_devices
    This RPC returns the number of devices attached to a basestation
    Rpc_login
    This RPC returns a login token if the login credentials are valid.
    Rpc_set_device_name
    This RPC sets the human readable name of a device
